    {
      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-8048-9a4e-f53b1a6c7dd0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To take advantage of this phenomenon, the authors introduce an option-weighted enhanced mixture-of-experts knowledge tracing (WEKT) method. Each answer receives a specific weight and can be used to update the learners’ knowledge states. The structure combines cognitive theory and deep learning. Experiments on multiple datasets show that the model achieves its aims. ",
